The Paris and Kelvin projects which is the official reference projects for VSCP using the PIC microprocessor
has been moved to github and both also have there own documentation pages.

The Paris module is documented here  http://www.grodansparadis.com/paris/paris.html and it's repository
is here https://github.com/grodansparadis/can4vscp_paris

The Kelvin NTC module is documented here http://www.grodansparadis.com/kelvinntc10k/kelvin_ntc10ka.html
and it's repository is here https://github.com/grodansparadis/can4vscp_kelvin_ntc10k

The VSCP PIC1 bootloader for PIC18F devices can be found here https://github.com/grodansparadis/vscp_pic1_bootloader


Both Kelvin and Paris can be bought ready built or as bar pcb's from Grodans Paradis AB  http://www.frogshop.se